project_descr: Natura 2000 – Completion of Nature Protection Facilities

outputs.output_descr:
The project aims to provide support to the European Commission to complete the construction of nature protection facilities in three proposed Natura 2000 areas in the northern part of Cyprus. Nature protection facilities will include:
- Voluntary Centre of two units of buildings
- Visitor & Info Centre of two units of buildings
- Guard, Research & Rescue Centre of three units of buildings
